(26006, 'Rheumafen 100mg s.r.caps.', 'رومافين 100مجم كبسول', '', '13', 'Diclofenac sodium', 'Glaxo smithkline', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Nsaid.acetic acid derivatives', '100mg', 'Diclofenac is indicated for use in the treatment of pain and inflammation from varying sources including inflammatory conditions such as osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis, and ankylosing spondylitis, as well as injury-related inflammation due to surgery and physical trauma. It is often used in combination with [misoprostol] as a gastro-protective agent in patients with high risk of developing NSAID-induced ulcers.', '6221045000457', '', 893, '2022-12-08', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
